{"tid":1986063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 以羅志祥嘅跳舞實力 今時今日有冇機會喺韓國出道","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T16:53:48.000Z","uid":132174,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec87accd9934aa472d8d5148f60d8e564f225a1","tid":1986063,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"台灣野嚟講 小弟好誠實咁話你知我淨係聽周杰倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日終於睇過羅志祥嘅精舞門MV 話佢係亞洲舞王係咪吹大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就對跳舞一竅不通嘅當然唔敢踩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係淨係由體能消耗嚟講 我已經覺得佢啲舞比而家啲男團嗰啲輕鬆好多 (當然光速XX除外)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e862861d9cb2f6d112aec4e2aab24712b19dea","tid":1986063,"uid":205749,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"佢只係好似香港班中產藍絲咁<br />\n係當年舞風未盛行嘅年代出道 食到個勢<br />\n佢d咁嘅實力 喺韓國收得皮啦<br />\n佢而家仲有得跳 咪又係靠隊crew同公關"},{"pid":"bbda92903f4a7095a33fbbaf7b8f2b23de73b9fd","tid":1986063,"uid":27416,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"係韓星開左條歪路<br />\n無限加強舞蹈難度同時開極大伴唱<br />\n以前郭富城杜德偉羅志祥啲舞都唔難先唱到歌"},{"pid":"fd4bb01ceed541f4d53af7c704d86166919efbb7","tid":1986063,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e862861d9cb2f6d112aec4e2aab24712b19dea","tid":1986063,"uid":205749,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"佢只係好似香港班中產藍絲咁<br />\n係當年舞風未盛行嘅年代出道 食到個勢<br />\n佢d咁嘅實力 喺韓國收得皮啦<br />\n佢而家仲有得跳 咪又係靠隊crew同公關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"公關今日之後冇埋"},{"pid":"ea7391a4e09c5af47a56c85d1a16869485aae8ab","tid":1986063,"uid":183576,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bbda92903f4a7095a33fbbaf7b8f2b23de73b9fd","tid":1986063,"uid":27416,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"係韓星開左條歪路<br />\n無限加強舞蹈難度同